author: NPR Music
description:
Usually, @rubiomusic_'s voice floats through layers of reverb and effects. At her Tiny Desk, she stripped it all away and talked to us about the beauty of letting go and finding power in vulnerability.⁠
⁠
Host: Anamaria Sayre/NPR⁠
Producer: Pablo Valdivia/NPR⁠
Video: Sofia Seidel/NPR
title: @rubiomusic_ talked to us about the beauty of letting go and finding power in vulnerability.⁠⁠
